    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Artemidora <lb n="2"/>coniu<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>x</abbr></expan> cum fili<lb break="no" n="3"/>o suo et filia sua <lb n="4"/>Viventia patri eo<lb break="no" n="5"/>rum titulum posu<lb break="no" n="6"/>erunt </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>memoria Ne<lb break="no" n="3"/>potiani prin<lb break="no" n="4"/>cipalis vixit <lb n="5"/>annis XXX|<expan><ex>VI</ex><abbr>I</abbr></expan> Vic<lb break="no" n="6"/>tor <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> II <lb n="7"/>Iuli<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>na</abbr></expan> filia <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ixit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nis</ex></expan> III <lb n="8"/>Heraclius <expan><abbr>fra</abbr><ex>ter</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>vixit <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nis</ex></expan> III Vita<lb break="no" n="10"/>lis <expan><abbr>frat</abbr><ex>er</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> an<lb break="no" n="11"/>nis V <lb n="12"/>valete lecto<lb break="no" n="13"/>res
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>2 aneinanderpassende Fragmente erhalten. 2 Inschriftfelder: das obere mit bogenförmigem oberem Abschluß, das untere hochrechteckig. In den beiden oberen Ecken der Stele je ein Kranz. Z. 11: Sonderzeichen für VI ungefähr in Form eines G. (B): CIL 03, 13739: Z- 2: coniux sua A(?); Z. 11: XXX SI; Zahariade - Alexandrescu: Z. 12: an. II.</p>
            </div>
